name: Giftablee
overview:
Giftablee provides a simple way of maintaining and strengthening personal and professional social networks through sending gifts.

Our service enables people to connect with others beyond the virtual dimension and enables people to easily go the extra step through physical experience. Connect using your Facebook account and we will automatically import your friend and their info. You can also add contacts and events, and set custom reminders.

With Giftablee, you will never forget another special occasion. Save time when selecting gifts and strengthen relationships through gift giving.
